grade_preconditions.et:
In order to get a positive result (A, B, C, D, E) at the end of the semester, you need to:
1) participate actively in at least 23 classes (75% of all classes);
2) pass 2 classroom tests;
3) take and pass the Starditest and 2 preparation tests (pre-tests) in Moodle;
4) perform well in 2 speaking classes / an oral exam on topics "Mina ja minu õpingud" and "Minu kiire päev Tartus".
